{"type":"message","id":"5a4f47cd","parentId":"fe2fcd1d","timestamp":"2026-02-18T18:22:46.292Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-02-18 20:22 GMT+2] OPERATION: SYSTEM CORE UPGRADE V6 (SELF-MODIFICATION).\n\n1.  **Environment Sync (`openclaw.json`):**\n    *   *Act:* Edit `openclaw.json`. Add `env: { \"PATH\": \"${PATH}\", \"PYTHONIOENCODING\": \"utf-8\" }`.\n    *   *Verify:* This propagates system PATH to children.\n\n2.  **Global UTF-8 Fix:**\n    *   *Action:* Create `profile.ps1` (or equivalent init script if supported) containing `[Console]::OutputEncoding = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8`.\n    *   *Alternative:* Hardcode this into `agent_wrapper.py` startup sequence.\n\n3.  **Rust Core Integration:**\n    *   *Build:* Execute `cargo build --release` (assuming PATH works now).\n    *   *Install:* Copy `.dll` to `src/core/dmarket_rust_core.pyd`.\n    *   *Register:* Add `src/core` to `PYTHONPATH`.\n\n4.  **Doctor Skill Integration:**\n    *   *Migrate:* Move `scripts/doctor.py` to `skills/system-doctor/doctor.py`.\n    *   *Config:* Register `system-doctor` in `openclaw.json` skills list.\n\n5.  **Documentation (`docs/SYSTEM_UPGRADE_V6.md`):**\n    *   Log all architectural changes.\n\n6.  **Final Verification:**\n    *   Run `python skills/system-doctor/doctor.py`.\n    *   Run `cargo --version` (via wrapper)."}],"timestamp":1771438966290}}
